</game> ','rince of Persia: The Two Thrones is an action-adventure video game developed and published by Ubisoft Montreal. The game combines exploration and combat. Both elements make use of the Prince''s acrobatic capability and agility. Throughout much of the game, the player must attempt to traverse the palace by running across walls, ascending or descending chasms by jumping back and forth between walls, avoiding traps, climbing structures and jumping from platform to platform, making other types of well-timed leaps, solving puzzles and using discovered objects to progress. The Two Thrones marked the third and final chapter for The Sands of Time saga.','../../icons/70.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (71,'Psychonauts',0,2005,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/71.jpg','<game>
