	</rule>
</game> ','Neverwinter Nights 2 (also known as NWN2) is a role-playing video game developed by Obsidian Entertainment and published by Atari. It is the sequel to BioWare''s Neverwinter Nights, based on the Dungeons ' || chr(38) || ' Dragons pencil and paper fantasy role-playing game. Neverwinter Nights 2 utilizes an adaptation of the Dungeons ' || chr(38) || ' Dragons 3.5 edition rules.
Players create player characters to represent themselves during the game, using the same character creation rules as found in the Dungeons ' || chr(38) || ' Dragons game. They may gain the assistance of additional party members, and they eventually acquire a keep that can be used as a base of operations. Neverwinter Nights 2 is set in the Forgotten Realms campaign settingةn and around the city of Neverwinter. The story is mostly unrelated to Neverwinter Nights and follows the journey of an orphaned adventurer investigating a group of mysterious artifacts known as "silver shards" and their connection to an ancient, evil spirit known as the King of Shadows.','../../icons/166.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (167,'Icewind Dale: Enhanced Edition',0,2014,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/167.jpg','<game>
