Set in modern times in an enchanted tower named Temen-ni-gru, the story centers on the dysfunctional relationship between Dante and his brother Vergil. The events of the game take place just as Dante has opened up the Devil May Cry agency (unnamed at this point in the story), and before Dante''s demonic heritage has reached its full potential. The story is told primarily through a mixture of cutscenes using the game''s engine with several pre-rendered full motion videos.','../../icons/294.png');
