</game>','Kohan: Ahriman''s Gift (known as Kohan: Battles of Ahriman in Europe) is a stand-alone expansion pack for Kohan released on November 6, 2001. The game allows play from an evil perspective, with the player leading armies of Undead and Shadowbeasts. It introduces an improved AI, new units and three new campaigns, as well as some new multiplayer maps and modes. However, it has been criticized for not bringing enough new features to justify its cost.

