Play as 5 different class''s! Solder, Medic, Engineer, Field Ops, Covert Ops each with there own special items and ability''s. The Covert Ops can steal the uniforms of fallen enemies and perform covert reconnaissance behind enemy lines, while Engineers can plant and diffuse land mines as well as construct battlefield structures including bridges, guard towers and forward operations bases in the midst of combat to gain advantages for their team. Medics provide health and revive fallen teammates, as Field Ops use their binoculars to mark enemy positions for a Soldier''s mortar barrage. Each Axis or Allies team can divide itself into smaller fire teams for quick and easy communication using an intuitive messaging system and dynamic command map of the entire battlefield. Work along side your comrades to complete the mission objectives with in a given time limit. Play with custom maps or stock maps that will keep you entertained for hours on end.','../../icons/345.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (347,'South Park: The Stick of Truth',0,2014,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/347.jpg','<game>
