</game> ','Alien Swarm is a Source SDK game from a group of talented designers at Valve who were hired from the mod community. Available free of charge, this top-down tactical STG thrusts players into an epic bug hunt featuring a unique blend of co-op play and squad-level tactics. With your friends, form a squad of four distinct IAF Marine classes. Plan your attack using an unlockable arsenal of weapons with countless loadout configurations against a wide variety of aliens. Blaze your way through an overrun, off-world colony, eradicating the alien infestation in environments ranging from the icy planet''s surface, to a subterranean lava-flooded mining facility.','../../icons/454.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (463,'Age of Empires II: The Age of Kings',0,1999,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/463.jpg','<game>
