Lead one of three unique Asian civilizations -- Japan, China and India -- each with their own assortment of civ-specific units such as Samurai, Flamethrowers, and War Elephants, that impact how they are played. Inspired by Asia''s history, the expansion includes not only authentic units but also maps and buildings that reflect each civilization''s history and culture.','../../icons/468.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (469,'The Immortals of Terra: A Perry Rhodan Adventure',0,2008,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/469.jpg','<game>
