Force Reconnaissance Team ԒazorԠare among the first to fight. This elite five-man team are about to fall down the rabbit hole, trapped in a war not only for control of the country, but the hearts and minds of its people. With the might of the USMC offshore and the Russians anxiously watching from the north, the stakes couldn''t be higher. The fate of Chernarus is balanced on a razor''s edge...','../../icons/443.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (439,'America''s Army 3',0,2009,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/439.jpg','<game>
