</game> ','Built on Unreal Engine 3, America''s Army 3 delivers stunningly realistic characters, environments, lighting effects, animations, and team-based experiences. In a game where every detail counts, players are bound by Rules of Engagement (ROE) and gain experience as they navigate challenges in team-based, multiplayer, and force-on-force operations. With 15 different map/mission combinations and exclusive advanced training that allows you to unlock new abilities and customize your gear, you''ll experience soldiering in the U.S. Army like never before. America''s Army is the official game of the U.S. Army.','../../icons/439.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (444,'Tropico 3',0,2009,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/444.jpg','<game>
