	</rule>
	<rule>
		<proc>DXHRDC.exe</proc>
		<file>bigfile.000</file>
	</rule>
</game> ','Deus Ex: Human Revolution is an action RPG, the second sequel to 2000''s Deus Ex. You play Adam Jensen, a security specialist, handpicked to oversee the defense of one of Americaӳ most experimental biotechnology firms. But when a black ops team uses a plan you designed to break in and kill the scientists you were hired to protect, everything you thought you knew about your job changes. Customize and upgrade your character with more than 50 unique augmentations that support your style of play. Live the reactive and dangerous world: your choices will have consequences in the gameӳ world, and there are always multiple solutions to every challenge. The actions you take will lead to an ultimate decision on mankindӳ future.','../../icons/490.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (491,'Doc Clock: The Toasted Sandwich of Time',0,2011,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/491.jpg','<game>
