		<file>packages\s_cascade_game.pc</file>
	</rule>
</game> ','Immerse yourself in this addictive puzzler that''s all about strategically twisting and connecting mismatched dials to save precious droplitz. Just making a single junction is child''s play; can you master the art of the combo or will you let your pipes runneth over? Be warned: losing too many droplitz can be hazardous to your ability to win. With four unique play modes, a variety of board sizes, and infinite replayability, Droplitz promises to drain all your time away.','../../icons/524.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (525,'Eets',0,2006,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/525.jpg','<game>
