</game> ','Bringing the legendary war between two of science fiction''s most popular characters to first-person shooter fans, Aliens vs. Predator delivers three outstanding single player campaigns and provides untold hours of unique 3-way multiplayer gaming. The Aliens, Predators, and Colonial Marines each have their own storyline that together form one story. Experience distinctly new and thrilling first-person action as you survive, hunt, and prey in the deadly jungles and swamps surrounding the damned colony of Freya''s Prospect.','../../icons/526.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (528,'Shadowgrounds Survivor',0,2007,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/528.jpg','<game>
