</game>','Anachronox is a 2001 third-person CRPG that follows the adventures of Sylvester "Sly" Boots, a down-on-his-luck detective trying to repay a hefty debt. Taking a simple assignment as a bodyguard, Sly finds himself caught up in much larger events, and the fate of the universe is placed in his unlikely hands. It is notable for being one of the first CRPGs to be designed according to console-oriented JRPG sensibilities; the game was inspired by titles such as Final Fantasy VII.','../../icons/1342.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (1343,'The Matrix: Path of Neo',0,2005,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/1343.jpg','<game>
