</game> ','Dwarf Fortress is a part construction and management simulation, part roguelike, freeware indie video game. The primary game mode is set in a procedurally generated fantasy world in which the player indirectly controls a group of dwarves and attempts to construct a successful and wealthy underground fortress.','../../icons/535.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (1349,'Dynasty Warriors 8: Xtreme Legends',0,2013,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/1349.jpg','<game>
