Red Alert 2 is the next in the Command and Conquer series of real-time strategy game. Play as either Allied or Soviet forces and command armies composed of various specialized units.','../../icons/536.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (538,'Command ' || chr(38) || ' Conquer 3: Tiberium Wars',0,2007,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/538.jpg','<game>
	<rule>
		<proc>CNC3.exe</proc>
		<file>cnc3game.dat</file>
	</rule>
</game> ','The year is 2047. A massive nuclear fireball explodes high in the night sky, marking the dramatic beginning of the Third Tiberium War and the long-awaited return of the most groundbreaking Real-Time Strategy franchise of all time. Command ' || chr(38) || ' Conquer 3 Tiberium Wars unveils the future of RTS gaming by bringing you back to where it all began: the Tiberium Universe. With the corrupt substance Tiberium blanketing most of the Earth, the infamous Kane is back to lead his Brotherhood of Nod in a massive global assault on the Global Defense Initiative (GDI) and the few remaining livable Blue Zones left on the planet. Only you can stop him. Featuring state-of-the-art next-generation graphics, an epic story, and truly innovative features such as the ability to transform online battles into a spectator sport, Command ' || chr(38) || ' Conquer is about to reinvent RTS gaming Šagain. Welcome back, Commander.','../../icons/538.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (274,'The Sims 2: Mansion and Garden Stuff',0,2008,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/274.jpg','<game>
