</game>','Giants: Citizen Kabuto is a third-person shooter with real-time strategy elements developed by Planet Moon Studios. Players take control of a single character from one of three humanoid races to complete the story or to challenge other players in online multiplayer matches. They can select heavily armed Meccaryns equipped with jet packs, or amphibious spellcasting Sea Reapers. "Citizen Kabuto" refers to the last selectable race, a thundering behemoth who can execute earthshaking professional wrestling attacks to pulverize its enemies.','../../icons/1153.png');
