</game>','From the creators of the critically-acclaimed Need for Speed Underground series, Need for Speed Most Wanted combines the thrill of street racing and tuner customization with the intensity of police pursuits. Need for Speed Most Wanted challenges you to become the most notorious street racer by exploiting a wide-open environment to elude rivals and cops.
Get in the driverӳ seat of the most sought-after race carsةncluding tuners, exotics, muscle cars, and other sports carsءnd experience high-speed, open-world street racing at its best. Tune your ride, win races, evade cops, become the most wanted.','../../icons/925.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (926,'Need for Speed: The Run',0,2011,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/926.jpg','<game>
