</game> ','"Yuri''s Revenge" is an expansion to the Real-Time-Strategy-Game "Red Alert 2", that takes place shortly after the allied campaign of Red Alert 2.
After the allies have won the war against the Soviet Union, Yuri - an ex-Soviet scientist, turned dictator - reveals his plan to enslave humanity with his invention called the "Psychic Dominator."
