The game''s twisty plot leads our naive hero on a hilarious, swash-buckling search for the fabled secret of Monkey Island. Tales of pirate wealth lure him to the port of M뭩e with high hopes, no money, and insatiable curiosity. If clever enough, he will win the confidence of M뭩e''s pirates and find himself blown by the winds of fate toward the terrifying and legendary Monkey Island -- an adventure that would chill the bones of even the most bloodthirsty buccaneer.
Adventure game developed and released by Lucas Arts.','../../icons/1002.png');
