Recipient of numerous awards, including 2006 Best First Person Shooter and Best Online Game, Tom Clancy''s Rainbow Six Vegas 2 pushes the top-selling franchise to new heights with new gameplay features and groundbreaking co-op and multiplayer modes.','../../icons/523.png');
