</game>','Rune is a third-person hack-and-slash game developed by Human Head Studios. The game is based on Norse mythology, showing the conflict between the gods Odin and Loki and the build up to Ragnarok, the end of the world. The game casts the player as Ragnar, a young Viking warrior. The various enemies Ragnar faces include, among others, man-eating fish, goblins, zombies, Norse dwarves, and other Vikings.','../../icons/1165.png');
Insert into GAMETRACE.GAME (GAMEID,GAMENAME,GAMEPC,GAMERY,GAMEPSEC,GAMEPMIN,GAMEPHOUR,GAMEPDAY,GAMEPN,GIMG,GAMEDR,GAMEDESC,GAMEICON) values (1166,'Painkiller: Hell ' || chr(38) || ' Damnation',0,2012,0,0,0,0,0,'../../games/1166.jpg','<game>
