</game>','Michel Ancel, the celebrated creator of Rayman, Beyond Good ' || chr(38) || ' Evil, and the Raving Rabbids, returns to unleash his innovative creativity on this new entry into the Rayman franchise.
When Rayman, Globox, and the Teensies discover a mysterious tent filled with captivating paintings, they are suddenly transported to a series of mythical new worlds!
