Choose one of 16 locations for your very first golf club. Build the perfect course by creating rolling fairways, lush greens and strategically placed water hazards. Make it your own by raising and lowering terrain, adding Japanese gardens and scenic landmarks! Keep golfers happy with everything from ball washers and pro shops to luxury hotels and casinos. Create your own golf pro and then test your course. Customize each golfer with a unique name, personality, appearance and dialogue. Trade your courses and golf stories with other SimGolf players around the world.','../../icons/970.png');
